# EldenRimTogether Wabbajack Changelog
=======================================

**Mod Organizer 2 Version ::** 2.5.2 ML1.5 (Windows), 2.5.2 (Windows)
**RootBuilder Version ::** 5.0.5.0

**SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS ::** A PC I guess

### Changelog Legend ::
```
+ = Added Mod
- = Removed Mod
E = Enabled Mod
D = Disabled Mod
M = Modified Mod (Give summary of changes)
// = Comment (Yes C comments)
```

