# Version 3.4.1

06/06/2026 XX:XX UTC :: SKSE Launch - Untested | STR Launch - Untested
// Version 3.4.1 hotfix - CTD fix + skill system cleanup + new NPC replacers + missed Nexus updates + new conditional sneak animations
// dTry Plugin Updates disabled: it ships EldenParry.dll which looks for a now-missing ESP, causing CTDs. Parry for All is the active parry system on this branch while we test
// Static Skill Leveling stack + Custom Skills Framework stack disabled: NEW SKILL MENU integrates both natively, so the standalone stacks are redundant
// DnD-XP stack disabled for testing: STR multiplayer level desync (e.g. one player can leave Bleak Falls at lvl 5 while their party member somehow leaves at lvl 35)
// APAS Reborn AP Voice Addon Patch installed as its own folder so it can't accidentally overwrite AP Reborn (same Nexus page hosts both)
// DVA - Better Vampires Patch installed as its own folder so it can't accidentally overwrite DVA (same shared-page pattern as APAS Reborn)
// NPC Spell Variance - Vanilla Runes for Spellcasters (SPID) installed as its own folder for the same reason - shared Nexus page with the base mod
// Milfactory College of Winterhold replacers: author came back and dropped the new MCW set
// BHUNP Skyrim Vanilla Outfits hotfix 2.3.0.0b added per author
// Dynamic Relaxed Sneak OAR added - new conditional animation set from the Modesty author, same style; OAR integration for Vanilla Sneak Animations pulled in as its required dependency
